{"data":[{"name":"104:1","price":"伤哉！每个诽谤者，诋毁者，","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6180,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"104:2","price":"他聚积财产, 而当作武器，","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6181,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"104:3","price":"他以为他的财产，能使他不灭。","arabic":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6182,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"104:4","price":"绝不然，他必定要被投在毁灭坑中。","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6183,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"104:5","price":"你怎能知道毁灭坑是什么？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6184,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"104:6","price":"是安拉的燃着的烈火。","arabic":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6185,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"104:7","price":"能升到人的心上。","arabic":"ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6186,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"104:8","price":"他们必定要被关在烈火中，","arabic":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6187,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"104:9","price":"吊在许多高柱子上。","arabic":"فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6188,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah","Chapter Al-Humazah","Humazah","Surah Humazah","Chapt